description: The Property is a well-cared for three-family building ideally located on the East Side of South Boston. Marble bathrooms, stainless steel appliances, honed granite countertops, in-unit laundry, and private outdoor space off each unit and large shared backyard. Spacious bedrooms throughout all three units. This building benefits from being situated in one of Boston’s fastest growing and diverse submarkets.
